{"tid":1470681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[以正視聽] 818 勇武和理非一齊出黎","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:16:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:41:01.000Z","uid":61886,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"4909c579b728482e4ab3b92ca6beb3ff5c6799da","tid":1470681,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:16:29.000Z","msg":"點解要講明勇武唔好出黎<br />\n<br />\n自己友開post都標籤晒勇武<br />\n<br />\n仲要講到勇武出黎會搞事<br />\n<br />\n勇武只係心理勇武<br />\n<br />\n其實好多都係和理非慢慢轉變做勇武<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想講<br />\n<br />\n勇武好 和理非好 都係手足 都係香港人<br />\n<br />\n818 一齊出黎"},{"pid":"41fec61f9e64cf589a34f0ff175e9bcdcf5dabe6","tid":1470681,"uid":53062,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:17:41.000Z","msg":"勇武和理非不是群體<br />\n是能力，警愓對家標籤分化"},{"pid":"f16f5de76ee2e710604d2aaa5a96fe5ebf4bbdf4","tid":1470681,"uid":43657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fcc740630595d511a50db291bb9e4b9bb2243cc","tid":1470681,"uid":61886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:17:51.000Z","msg":"我自己都企過唔少次前線<br />\n<br />\n其實前線手足都好願意互相討論"},{"pid":"f7bb771ece0e33bf68635ee830b9cfa41d935024","tid":1470681,"uid":61886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:18:57.000Z","msg":"你可以叫勇武手足唔好圍狗屋<br />\n<br />\n但點可以叫佢地唔好出黎<br />\n<br />\n問心<br />\n<br />\n勇武手足見到係咩感受"},{"pid":"a30cf197a509ed93b6c1a44240e971f0d4cb2929","tid":1470681,"uid":288912,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:18:59.000Z","msg":"和理非到今日都未認錯，勇武再出嚟會唔會變condom?"},{"pid":"b726bc2cb87134b855752ff0b5d525b82bb5516f","tid":1470681,"uid":291461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:19:02.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家跟實原定路線 等啲狗狗數清楚有幾多人 前面停左行唔到就唔郁"},{"pid":"bbb1f7f0e06b5ac5b05f7a50f6fcb1bb16d1fa63","tid":1470681,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:19:12.000Z","msg":"勇武既都會遊行"},{"pid":"13d032a91c295579293a0840ac8813605c7415db","tid":1470681,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:20:38.000Z","msg":"大家互相依靠<br />\n<br />\n有人開post分化就唔得"},{"pid":"c28346626fa8b99394b264b42c00f9a246ba917c","tid":1470681,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"大家都係香港人，不用分那麼細<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非、勇武唔係人嘅標籤，而係行為性質<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470297\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470297</a>"},{"pid":"108c89ffbfe3817d26e3cb7a65bdc82d15b82bd4","tid":1470681,"uid":76941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:21:21.000Z","msg":"勇武同和理非只係心態上既分別<br />\n大家都係手足<br />\n不分化不割席<br />\n818見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672ad9b25ded53f4413b3a107a208c0a472b846a","tid":1470681,"uid":265904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"果日唔圍狗局, 唔SET ROAD BLOCK , 行完走勇武派係咪會先?<br />\n民陣係講明真係行完散, 如果當日想勇武既可以留番下次先?<br />\n<br />\n我知, 一定又SPIN 番去, 「幾時仲有下次」 「和埋非有撚用咩」呢條問題, 之後下半場又再SET ROAD BLOCK , 圍狗局, 落單送頭。"},{"pid":"05662914839b80a7589aca121d8c0583fa960757","tid":1470681,"uid":39796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:23:37.000Z","msg":"不了<br />\n和理非實第一時間走人<br />\n然後勇武被拉<br />\n連登又會恥笑 &amp; 憤怒兩天<br />\n下星期報仇又民意上身了"},{"pid":"97ce417ef051e857338b05a4cd1c34110efac71c","tid":1470681,"uid":31491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:23:54.000Z","msg":"出黎係好<br />\n但應該集中返用遊行表達訴求 暫時停一次勇武行動<br />\n如果唔係最後政府同市民又focus係勇武果邊<br />\n成個遊行會少左好多影響力"},{"pid":"06a4a49789f17511a36775eaf64f2a2e18ceb8f5","tid":1470681,"uid":61886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"97ce417ef051e857338b05a4cd1c34110efac71c","tid":147068